
4. Database
***********

4.1 Description
===============

The PyMSA database is developed to work with both MySQL and SQLite. To make the SQLite database, run createDatabase.py from pyMSA/database/. To make the MySQL database,
use the MySQL_create_pyMSA_database.sql file (on MySQL commandline: mysql> source /path/to/PyMSA/database/MySQL_create_pyMSA_database.sql.
See usage for how to change between SQLite and MySQL when filling or querying the database. 

